      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@\n+# CLAUDE.md\n+\n+This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.\n+\n+## Project Overview\n+\n+This is the **Tenzir Library**, a collection of open-source packages for Tenzir\u2014a security data pipeline platform. Each package provides reusable TQL (Tenzir Query Language) components for ingesting, parsing, transforming, and mapping security logs to OCSF (Open Cybersecurity Schema Framework)."
